messages.body:
How many Germans does it take to change a lightbulb?
Just the one, because they are very efficient and they don't have a sense of humour.

Did you hear about the person who spent over £1 million in the perfume shop?
They had more money than scents.

My uncle just died.
He fell into a vat of polish at the furniture factory. It was a terrible end but a lovely finish.

My boyfriend bought me a diamond ring The stone was cut in the shape of a four leaf clover. I wore it all the time to show how much it meant to me.
One day, I got curious and had it valued at a jeweller's. Unfortunately they told me that my boyfriend had been swindled, as the diamond was actually a cubic zirconia.It was a sham rock.

If you lose one of your senses, your other senses get enhanced
This is why people with no sense of humor have a heightened sense of self'importance.

What do wounded alligators drink?
Gatorade

When I heard Justin Bieber has Lyme disease, I almost felt sorry for the annoying, creepy little parasite.
Can't say the same about Bieber though.

Why is it getting harder to buy Advent calendars?
Their days are numbered

A man walks into a vacuum cleaner store
After browsing around for a while, he asked to see the manager. When the manager came, he asked, "Is there something wrong?" And then the man replied with, "Oh something's wrong alright. Everything you sell sucks!"

A Nun was taking a bath when there was a knock at the door. "Who is it?" She asked. The voice back replies "It's the blind man, can I come in?" The Nun thinks for a moment and says "yes that's fine". The door opens and the man says.
Nice tits, where you want me to hang the blinds?

How do you know the Japanese mass murderer was a chef?
He spent his day cutting up vegetables

The creator of the USB flash drive died today.
He was lowered into his coffin, flipped over, and then lowered again.

Anyone who thought Trump was gonna pull the US out of the middle east is an idiot.
I mean if he was any good at pulling out, he probably wouldn't have 5 kids.

Little Red Riding Hood walks alone through the dark forest.
Suddenly she hears a rustling behind a thick bush.She pushes the branches and bushes aside and suddenly the big bad wolf is sitting in front of her."Oh, bad wolf. Why do you have such big red eyes?""Get out of here. I'm pooping!"

I'm not sure how much you know about the story of the Titanic...
...but what caused it to sink is just the tip of the iceberg.

Who Did Fonzie call when his motorcycle broke down?
Triple Ayyy!

At the mall today I saw a toddler gnawing on a small rubber duck.
I asked him if it tasted like quackers.

What are ghosts favorite thing to read?
BOOks

TIL: In the movie “The Day After Tomorrow”, the scene involving people migrating illegally into Mexico involve dozens of extras actually crossing from the USA into Mexico over the Rio Grande
Fortunately, all 1673 of them safely made it back to the US side without issue.

When wearing a bikini, a woman reveals 90 % of her body
Men are so polite that they only look at the covered part.

All the comic books I inherited from my older brother had their last pages missing.
I had to draw my own conclusions.

I asked my biology teacher how he makes his class so interesting
He told me: Sex cells.

What do window washers, who are high on really good weed, deal with every day?
Chronic pane

I am thinking about opening a dungeons and dragons themed vacation rental...
I’m going to call it Air D&D

I bought a Microsoft advent calendar...
But if you open too many windows at once, they shut down for no fucking reason.
